  "//": "Shared scenario spec for the agent-loop event-order oracle (PLAN 5.4). tests/agent-parity/gen-oracle.ts drives pi's real Agent/agent-loop.ts; tests/agent-parity/driver.lua replays the same cases through pi.agent.new. Both sides synthesize identical scripted stream events from each turn spec (start, per-block start/delta/end, done|error; abort check before every push), identical scripted tools (per-invocation updates/sleeps/results/throws, abortCheck), and identical hook scripts ({skip:true} means 'return nothing' because JSON null cannot cross the Lua boundary). Triggers fire synchronously inside the recording listener when the Nth event of a type is observed. Timestamps are scrubbed to 0 on both sides.",
